1 AN ACT concerning
2 Environment – Coal Combustion By–Products – Fees, Coordinating Committee,
3 and Regulations
4 FOR the purpose of providing that a certain base fee established by the Department of the
5 Environment that is paid by a certain generator of coal combustion by–products is
6 not less than a certain amount; altering the factors that the Department of the
7 Environment is required to consider in establishing a certain fee; requiring the
8 Department to use certain excess fees collected from certain generators of coal
9 combustion by–products for certain purposes; establishing the Statewide Coal
10 Combustion By–Products Coordinating Committee to share information, monitoring
11 results, and certain remedial actions with respect to certain coal combustion
12 by–product sites; requiring the Department to adopt certain regulations on or before
13 a certain date to implement a certain federal guidelines and rules rule; and generally
14 relating to the regulation of coal combustion by–products in the State.
